--     milkshake/shake/can/iced boost → beverages, everything else → food).
--   • Combos (item names containing '+') are classified as food.
--   • ON CONFLICT (entry_date) DO NOTHING — never overwrites an existing day.
--     Drop the conflict clause and use DO UPDATE if you want overwrite semantics.
